Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-white-house-aides-drop-out-election-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrumbles%20behind%20closed%20doors%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20Thursday%2C%20Biden's%20top%20campaign%20advisors%20explained%20that%20they%20still%20have%20multiple%20paths%20to%20the%20270%20electoral%20votes%20needed%20to%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20internal%20data%20and%20public%20polling%20show%20the%20same%20thing%3A%20this%20remains%20a%20margin-of-error%20race%20in%20key%20battleground%20states%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden's%20campaign%20chair%20Jen%20O'Malley%20Dillon%20and%20campaign%20manager%20Julie%20Chavez%20Rodriguez%20wrote%20in%20a%20memo%20to%20staffers%20that%20was%20first%20published%20by%20The%20Associated%20Press%20and%20later%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20conceded%20that%20the%20debate%20had%20been%20a%20setback%20for%20the%20president%20but%20argued%20it%20was%20far%20too%20early%20to%20count%20him%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b22fad92-94ee-48b0-870d-beb67ec00cd9%5C%22%3EBiden%20in%20his%20wheelhouse%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20good%20news%20for%20Biden%20is%20that%20the%20news%20conference%20set%20him%20up%20in%20his%20wheelhouse%3A%20foreign%20policy.%20As%20a%20US%20senator%2C%20Biden%20served%20on%20the%20powerful%20Senate%20Foreign%20Relations%20Committee%20for%20decades%20and%20eventually%20rose%20to%20lead%20the%20panel.%20President%20Barack%20Obama%20praised%20Biden's%20knowledge%20of%20world%20affairs%20when%20he%20tapped%20him%20as%20his%20running%20mate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20pundits%20and%20journalists%20acknowledged%20his%20command%20of%20the%20issues.%20But%20there%20is%20still%20concern%20%E2%80%94%20even%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpuck.news%2Fpost-biden-debate-view-from-nato-summit%2F%3Futm_source%3Dtwitter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEuropeans%20at%20the%20NATO%20summit%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20about%20