%2C%20laughed%20it%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFellow%20leaders%20at%20the%20summit%20have%20fielded%20questions%20about%20Biden%2C%20and%20their%20answers%20have%20largely%20been%20supportive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSlips%20of%20the%20tongue%20happen%2C%20and%20if%20you%20keep%20a%20close%20enough%20eye%20on%20everyone%2C%20you%20will%20find%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20German%20Chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%20said%20after%20the%20president's%20latest%20gaffe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrench%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20said%20Biden%20had%20appeared%20%26quot%3Bin%20charge%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bwas%20on%20good%20form.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20latest%20verbal%20slip%20could%20not%20have%20come%20at%20a%20worse%20time%20as%20Biden%20is%20due%C2%A0%20later%20Thursday%20to%20give%20what%20the%20White%20House%20has%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20boy%26quot%3B%20press%20conference%2C%20his%20first%20major%20appearance%20since%20the%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20solo%20appearance%2C%20a%20rare%20unscripted%20encounter%20with%20reporters%2C%20comes%20amid%20growing%20calls%20in%20his%20Democratic%20Party%20for%20him%20to%20step%20aside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20press%20conference%20was%20due%20to%20start%20at%206%3A30%20pm%20(2230%20GMT)%20but%20is%20expected%20to%20run%20around%20an%20hour%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20Growing%20pressure%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20steady%20drumbeat%20of%20Democrats%20calling%20for%20Biden%20to%20abandon%20his%202024%20candidacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHollywood%20actor%20and%20well-connected%20Democratic%20supporter%20George%20Clooney%20called%20on%20Biden%20to%20exit%20the%20race%2C%20and%20party%20grandee%20Nancy%20Pelosi%20has%20stopped%20short%20of%20fully%20backing%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2014%20Democratic%20members%20of%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives%20have%20openly%20urged%20the%20man%20who%20beat%20Trump%