t.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fbeastie-boys-lawsuit-chilis-sabotage-ads-1236067988%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fbeastie-boys-lawsuit-chilis-sabotage-ads-1236067988%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Air%20Vistara%3A%20An%20Aviation%20Icon%20Fades%20Away%2C%20And%20The%20Chaos%20It%20Leaves%20Behind%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fj7auhnbg_vistara_625x300_12_July_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2010%2C%202022%2C%20we%20were%20booked%20in%20Business%20Class%20to%20Dubai%20on%20Air%20India.%20Upon%20reaching%20the%20check-in%20counter%2C%20we%20were%20informed%20that%20five%20seats%20in%20business%20class%20were%20broken.%20Consequently%2C%20we%20were%20offered%20extra%20legroom%20seats%20in%20economy%20class%20while%20retaining%20our%20business%20class%20seats%20for%20the%20next%20flight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20staff%20tried%20to%20reassure%20us%20that%20it%20would%20be%20fine%20for%20a%20short%20flight%2C%20but%20we%20had%20important%20meetings%20scheduled%20in%20Dubai%20the%20following%20morning%2C%20so%20we%20declined.%20After%20learning%20that%20the%20issue%20was%20with%20the%20TVs%2C%20we%20expressed%20that%20we%20didn't%20mind%20as%20we%20just%20wanted%20to%20sleep.%20Despite%20this%2C%20we%20were%20forced%20to%20write%20a%20letter%20stating%20we%20had%20no%20objection%20to%20flying%20with%20broken%20seats%20in%20business%20class%20to%20avoid%20future%20claims%20for%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20my%20first%20experience%20with%20Air%20India%20post%20the%20Tata%20takeover.%20As%20we%20boarded%20the%20flight%2C%20we%20saw%20empty%20business-class%20seats.%20Interestingly%2C%20just%20before%20take-off%2C%20five%20people%20in%20pilots'%20uniforms%20occupied%20the%20supposedly%20broken%20seats%2C%20leaving%20business%20class%20fully%20occupied.%20The%20TV%20in%20my%20seat%2C%20which%20was%20claimed%20to%20be%20non-functional%2C%20worked%20perfectly%20fine.%20It%20was%20clear%20this%20was%20done%20to%20accommodate%20their%20own%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20easy%20to%20dwell%20on%20negative%20experiences%2C%20there%20was%20a%20positive%20aspect%20to%20this%20journey.%20On%20our%20return%20flight%20on%20December%2013%2C%20which%20was%20a%20midnight%20flight%2C%20it%20was%20my%20daughter's%20birthday.%20The%20Air%20India%20crew%20overheard%20this%20and%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20usual%20welcome%20drink%2C%20they%20brought%20champagne%20for%20all%20of%20us%20to%20celebrate%20even%20before%20we%20took%20off.%20This%20thoughtful%20gesture%20was%20indeed%20touching.%20When%20I%20inquired%20whether%20this%20change%20was%20due%20to%20the%20Tata%20takeover%2C%20the%20crew%20responded%20that%20this%20was%20always%20how%20Air%20India%20operated%2C%20which%20was%20intriguing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Does%20Air%20India%20Stand%20For%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20am%20not%20an%20aviation%20expert%2C%20my%20background%20in%20hospitality%20and%20customer%20service%20makes%20me%20appreciate%20organisations%20focused%20on%20service%20excellence.%20Transforming%20Air%20India%20is%20indeed%20an%20uphill%20task%2C%20but%20with%20dedicated%20efforts%2C%20it%20holds%20the%20potential%20for%20significant%20improvement%20and%20success.%20My%20friends%20working%20in%20the%20transformation%20team%20are%20committed%20to%20changing%20the%20airline%2C%20but%20culture%20is%20not%20built%20in%20a%20day.%20It%20takes%20years%20and%20positive%20reinforcement%20of%20company%20values.%20What%20does%20Air%20India%20stand%20for%3F%20Even%20they%20are%20struggling%20with%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20understand%20where%20Air%20India%20was%20before%20the%20Tata%20Group%20buyout.%20Air%20India%20operates%20over%20140%20aircraft%2C%20most%20of%20which%20are%20over%20a%20decade%20old%20and%20have%20never%20been%20refurbished.%20Airline%20veterans%20say%20that%20every%20seven%20to%20eight%20years%2C%20there%20should%20be%20a%20full%20refurbishment%20to%20keep%20the%20cabin%20fresh%20and%20functional.%20With%20broken%20seats%20and%20worn-out%20interiors%2C%20there%20is%20a%20significant%20problem%2C%20as%20there%20are%20no%20spare%20parts%20available%2C%20taking%20up%20to%2018%20months%20to%20get%20replacements.%20For%20example%2C%20even%20when%20the%20new%20flight%20on%20the%20Zurich%20to%20Delhi%20sector%20launched%20on%20June%2016%2C%20my%20daughter%20was%20informed%20that%2012%20seats%20in%20business%20class%20were%20broken.%20Competing%20with%20Swiss%20Air%20from%20Zurich%2C%20which%20has%20great%20aircraft%20and%20service%2C%20Air%20India's%20branding%20suffers%20as%20people%20are%20unlikely%20to%20return%20after%20a%20poor%20first%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Vistara%20Shutdown%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20blunders%20by%20the%20Tata%20Group%20is%20shutting%20down%20Vistara.%20The%20merger%20with%20Air%20India%20is%20poorly%20executed%20and%20ill-timed.%20The%20government%20and%20the%20Tata%20Group%20were%20aware%20that%20Air%20India%20was%20a%20defunct%20asset%20with%20old%2C%20tired%20planes%2C%20yet%20they%20approved%20the%20merger%20plan%20for%20short-term%20financial%20gain.%20Why%20couldn't%20the%20merger%20have%20been%20postponed%20for%20two%20years%3F%20The%20financial%20burden%20of%20maintaining%20Vistara%20could%20have%20been%20justified%20by%20its%20operational%20excellence%20and%20newer%20planes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVistara%2C%20with%20its%20reputation%20for%20service%20excellence%20and%2070%20new%20planes%2C%20contrasts%20sharply%20with%20Air%20India's%20outdated%20fleet.%20It%20is%20baffling%20that%20the%20Civil%20Aviation%20Ministry%20allowed%20the%20merger%20of%20a%20modern%2C%20well-functioning%20airline%20like%20Vistara%20with%20an%20outdated%20one%20and%20has%20approved%20Tata's%20decision%20to%20rebrand%20it%20as%20Air%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoor%20product%20and%20poor%20communication%20are%20two%20significant%20issues.%20Air%20India%20should%20conduct%20a%20masterclass%20on%20how%20not%20to%20communicate%20while%20running%20a%20consumer%20company.%20I%20recently%20travelled%20from%20Delhi%20to%20Hyderabad%20on%20Air%20India.%20The%20aircraft%20was%20fine%20and%20the%20service%20was%20great.%20But%20there%20was%20a%20communication%20problem.%20The%20flight%20was%20supposed%20to%20take%20off%20at%209%3A40%20am%2C%20but%20it%20took%20off%2040%20minutes%20later%20without%20any%20announcement.%20The%20crew%20later%20informed%20us%20that%20a%20connecting%20flight%20from%20Amsterdam%20had%20passengers%20boarding%20this%20flight.%20This%20could%20have%20been%20communicated%20to%20all%20passengers%20so%20everyone%20knows%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERespecting%20Public%20Opinion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20India%20needs%20a%20communication%20protocol.%20Weekly%20updates%20on%20the%20fleet%2C%20on-time%20performance%2C%20and%20consistency%20on%20social%20media%20channels%20can%20help%20shift%20consumer%20opinion.%20Public%20opinion%20overwhelmingly%20suggests%20that%20the%20merger%20was%20a%20mistake.%20The%20Tata%20Group%2C%20the%20Competition%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20and%20the%20Civil%20Aviation%20Ministry%20could%20have%20conducted%20a%20small%20consumer%20survey.%20My%20tweet%20on%20this%20received%20overwhelming%20responses%20-%20over%2095%25%20felt%20that%20Vistara%20and%20Air%20India%20should%20not%20have%20merged.%20Recent%20mishandling%20cases%20in%20Air%20India%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20long%20waits%20or%20lack%20of%20communication%2C%20highlight%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20transformation%20team%20at%20Air%20India%20is%20under%20immense%20pressure%2C%20trying%20their%20best.%20Building%20a%20culture%20of%20service%20excellence%20takes%20time.%20With%20the%20sudden%20merger%20of%20a%20well-functioning%20airline%20with%20an%20old%20one%2C%20the%20hope%20is%20that%20the%20amalgamation%20will%20create%20a%20better%20airline.%20However%2C%20why%20couldn't%20this%20merger%20wait%20for%2024%20months%3F%20In%20a%20resurgent%20India%2C%20this%20is%20a%20classic%20case%20of%20ignoring%20public%20opinion.%20Flying%20in%20India%20is%20becoming%20restricted%20to%20a%20duopoly%2C%20so%20the%20consumer's%20choice%20is%20limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conclusion%2C%20India%20faces%20challenging%20times%20in%20aviation.%20As%20a%20consumer%2C%20you%20have%20everything%20to%20lose%20post-September%2C%20when%20Vistara%20fades%20away.%20All%20you%20can%20do%20is%20pray%20that%20your%20Air%20India%20flight%20takes%20off%20on%20time%20and%20that%20you%20have%20a%20new%20plane.%20And%20do%20remember%2C%20good%20times%20don't%20last%20forever%2C%20the%20new%20feeling%20of%20flying%20Vistara%20is%20gone%20and%20dead%20too%20soon.%20The%20only%20silver%20lining%20is%20that%20even%20bad%20times%20don't%20last%20forever%2C%20and%20maybe%20Indigo%20and%20Akasa%20will%20take%20service%20excellence%20to%20new%20heights%2C%20till%20a%20resurgent%20Air%20India%20becomes%20the%20airline%20that%20you%20really%20want%20to%20be%20proud%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Kapil%20Chopra%20is%20the%20Founder%20of%20EazyDiner%2C%20India's%20most%20loved%20restaurant%20reservation%20app%20and%20The%20Postcard%20Hotel.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720732020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F57vgdbuo_vistara_625x300_12_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion