ainee%20IAS%20officer%20Puja%20Khedkar%2C%20caught%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20massive%20controversy%20over%20claims%20she%20made%20in%20her%20UPSC%20candidature%2C%20has%20properties%20worth%20crores%2C%20NDTV%20has%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Ms%20Khedkar's%20%26quot%3Bstatement%20of%20immovable%20property%20for%20the%20year%202023%26quot%3B%2C%20updated%20as%20of%20January%201%2C%202024%2C%20and%20exclusively%20accessed%20by%20NDTV%2C%20the%20junior%20officer%20owns%20five%20plots%20of%20land%20and%20two%20apartments%20across%20Maharashtra.%20The%20value%20of%20these%20assets%20totals%20a%20whopping%20Rs%2022%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F00tpvc9g_puja-khedkar-assets-ndtv_625x300_11_July_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disclosure%20lists%20her%20as%20the%20owner%20of%20two%20plots%20of%20land%20in%20Pune%20district's%20Mahalunge%20worth%20nearly%20Rs%2016%20crore%2C%20one%20in%20Pune%20district's%20Dhadawali%20worth%20Rs%204%20crore%2C%20and%20two%20in%20Ahmednagar's%20Pachunde%20and%20Nandur%20worth%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20and%20Rs%201%20crore%20respectively.%20The%20plots%20in%20Pachunde%20and%20Nandur%20were%20a%20gift%20from%20her%20mother.%20In%20all%2C%20she%20owns%20over%2022%20acres%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20has%20two%20apartments%20in%20Ahmednagar%20and%20Pune.%20The%20984-square-foot%20flat%20in%20Ahmednagar's%20Savedi%20is%20worth%20Rs%2045%20lakh%20and%20the%20724-square-foot%20apartment%20in%20Pune's%20Kondhwa%20is%20worth%20Rs%2075%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20assets%20were%20acquired%20between%202014%20and%202019%20and%20Ms%20Khedkar%20earns%20Rs%2042%20lakh%20annually%20from%20them.%20Moreover%2C%20according%20to%20Vijay%20Kumbhar%2C%20an%20RTI%20activist%20from%20Pune%2C%20her%20father%20has%20assets%20worth%20Rs%2040%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Khedkar%20posed%20as%20an%20OBC%20non-creamy%20layer%20candidate%20in%20her%20UPSC%20candidature.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20to%20qualify%20as%20an%20OBC%20non-creamy%20layer%20candidate%2C%20the%20annual%20income%20of%20the%20applicant's%20parents%20or%20the%20yearly%20income%20of%20the%20family%20should%20not%20be%20more%20than%20Rs%208%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Khedkar%2C%20who%20had%20an%20all-India%20rank%20of%20841%2C%20also%20claimed%20visual%20and%20mental%20disability.%20However%2C%20she%20did%20not%20undergo%20the%20mandatory%20medical%20tests%20to%20corroborate%20her%20disability%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20mounting%20trouble%20for%20the%20new%20IAS%20officer%2C%20the%20Centre%20has%20formed%20a%20single-member%20panel%20to%20verify%20the%20%26quot%3Bcandidature%20claims%20and%20other%20details%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20submitted.%20The%20committee%20will%20submit%20its%20report%20in%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202023-batch%20IAS%20officer%2C%20currently%20on%2024-month%20probation%2C%C2%A0is%20facing%20serious%20charges%20of%20impropriety%20and%20%26quot%3Babuse%20of%20power%26quot%3B.%20It%20is%20alleged%20that%20she%20was%20using%20a%20red-blue%20beacon%2C%20VIP%20number%20plates%2C%20and%20a%20%26quot%3BGovernment%20of%20Maharashtra%26quot%3B%20sticker%20on%20her%20private%20vehicle%2C%20an%20Audi%20sedan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20escalating%20row%2C%20Ms%20Khedkar%20has%20been%20transferred%20to%20Washim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGovernment%20rules%20do%20not%20allow%20me%20to%20speak%20anything%20on%20this%20matter.%20So%20sorry%2C%20I%20cannot%20speak%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20Khedkar%20told%20the%20media%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720714860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fvk5ojve8_puja-khedkar_625x300_10_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com