football%20world%20by%20storm.%20He%20became%20the%20youngest%20player%20to%20play%20and%20assist%20in%20a%20European%20Championship%20during%20Spain's%203-0%20win%20over%20Croatia.%20In%20the%20semi-final%2C%20Yamal%20scored%20against%20France%2C%20becoming%20the%20youngest%20player%20to%20score%20in%20Euros.%20Despite%20his%20achievements%2C%20German%20labour%20laws%20prevent%20him%20from%20playing%20full%20matches%20past%2011%20pm.%20Spain's%20coach%20faces%20challenges%20in%20managing%20his%20playtime%20to%20avoid%20fines%2C%20with%20the%20Euro%202024%20final%20posing%20a%20similar%20dilemma.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Ffootball%2Fuefa-euro-2024%2Feuro-2024-why-germanys-labour-law-is-prohibiting-lamine-yamal-to-play-for-90-minutes%2Farticleshow%2F111666779.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20the%20Man%20Preserving%20Traditional%20Himachali%20Architecture%20With%20His%20Dreamy%20Homestay%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20the%20beautiful%20city%20of%20Shimla%2C%20Rahul%20Bhushan%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20NORTH%2C%20a%20Himachal-based%20collective%20and%20homestay%2C%20disliked%20the%20rapid%20growth%20of%20modern%20architecture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPart%20of%20the%20reason%20was%20the%20rapid%20growth%20of%20the%20city%2C%20and%20part%20was%20the%20increase%20of%20tourism%20around%20these%20parts.%20I%20had%20always%20intended%20to%20return%20and%20do%20something%20to%20remind%20and%20highlight%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332067%2Fsustainable-home-mud-row-house-project-bengaluru-with-ecofriendly-architecture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20vernacular%20architecture%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rahul%20Bhushan%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20he%20runs%20a%20collective%20that%20hosts%20artists%E2%80%99%20residencies%20and%20acts%20as%20a%20regional%20centre%20that%20documents%20the%20architecture%2C%20way%20of%20life%2C%20regional%20culture%20and%20crafts%20of%20the%20region.%20The%20campus%20also%20doubles%20as%20a%20homestay%20which%20not%20only%20offers%20a%20peek%20into%20the%20beauty%20of%20the%20place%20but%20also%20the%20slow%20life%20of%20the%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20really%20wanted%20to%20have%20a%20holistic%20view%20of%20things%20and%20promote%20our%20culture%20and%20vernacular%20architecture%20while%20hosting%20people%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355205%2Fkerala-mud-homestay-mustafa-pa-converts-barren-mining-land-into-forest-greenara%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esustainable%20homestay%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20are%20sharing%20a%20way%20of%20life%20here%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENestled%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Naggar%2C%20amid%20the%20Deodar%20trees%2C%20the%20views%20that%20the%20homestay%20offers%20is%20like%20a%20dream%20come%20true.%20A%20visual%20delight%2C%20the%20place%20overlooks%20the%20Beas%20River%20and%20the%20majestic%20Dhauladhar%20range.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20magnificent%20homestay%20overlooking%20these%20views%20started%20as%20a%20collective%20to%20save%20the%20heritage%2C%20culture%20and%20vernacular%20architecture%20of%20the%20area.%20So%20what%20led%20to%20the%20foundation%20of%20this%20homestay%3F%20Rahul%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20my%20masters%20in%20architecture%2C%20I%20focused%20my%20research%20thesis%20on%20indigenous%20building%20practices%20in%20the%20western%20Himalayan%20region.%20I%20specifically%20looked%20at%20Kashmir%20and%20Himachal%20and%20documented%20the%20entire%20construction%20process.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20background%2C%20Rahul%20got%20the%20idea%20of%20using%20his%20knowledge%20for%20the%20holistic%20sustainable%20development%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295759%2Fbest-himalayan-treks-in-autumn-valley-of-flowers-kashmir-great-lakes-plan-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHimalayan%20region.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20so%20many%20buildings%20that%20can%20be%20restored%20and%20preserved.%20These%20buildings%20were%20built%20almost%20100%20years%20ago%2C%20some%20even%2080%20or%20150%20years%20ago.%20These%20buildings%20cannot%20be%20built%20again.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20traditional%20houses%20in%20local%20villages%2C%20and%20the%20Britishers%20also%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20buildings%20in%20Himachal.%20Unfortunately%2C%20these%20buildings%20are%20now%20being%20abandoned%20or%20slowly%20going%20out%20of%20use.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-25-1720707759.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20homestay%20is%20made%20of%20mud%2C%20clay%20and%20reclaimed%20wood.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-25-1720707759.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-25-1720707759-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-25-1720707759-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-25-1720707759-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F