0to%20see%20which%20ponds%20can%20be%20revived%20and%20create%20awareness%20about%20water%20conservation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Tiwari%20has%20a%20network%20of%205%2C000%20water%20friends%20across%20Bundelkhand.%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20not%20be%20around%20forever.%20I%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20that%20my%20work%20continues%20even%20if%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-6-1720083929.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Through%20the%20efforts%20and%20Tiwari%20and%20his%20friends%2C%20the%20Bajrang%20Sagar%20pond%20filled%20up%20with%20rainwater%20that%20lasted%20for%20a%20year%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-6-1720083929.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-6-1720083929-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-6-1720083929-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-6-1720083929-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-6-1720083929-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355544%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThrough%20the%20efforts%20of%20Tiwari%20and%20his%20friends%2C%20the%20Bajrang%20Sagar%20pond%20filled%20up%20with%20rainwater%20that%20lasted%20for%20a%20year%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Tiwari%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPowering%20through%20opposition%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3